These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-1::.
3 different games are played: chess, billiard, monopoly
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, rugby, surfing
1. the person who's sport is rugby is in the middle##1
2. the person playing monopoly is the person who's sport is surfing##1
3. the person playing chess is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |    3    |
| Game   | chess | billiard | monopoly   |
| Sport      | biathlon    | rugby  | surfing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-2::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, rugby, surfing
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, canadian, nigerian
1. the argentine is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
2. the canadian is on the far left##1
3. the canadian is the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Sport      | rugby | baseball     | surfing      |
| Nationality   | canadian | argentine | nigerian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-3::.
3 different pets are kept: horse, guinea-pig, chinchilla
There 3 different types of food: plum, radish, raspberry
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the person eating radish##1
2. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1
3. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person eating radish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Pet   | horse | chinchilla  | guinea-pig       |
| Food       | plum     | radish | raspberry |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-4::.
City: san-francisco, miami, hannover
The people have 3 different hobbies: card-games, puzzles, woodworking
1. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |      3      |
| City    | hannover    | miami     | san-francisco |
| Hobby   | woodworking | card-games | puzzles     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-5::.
3 different pets are kept: bird, guinea-pig, hedgehog
3 different games are played: canasta, backgammon, scrabble
1. the person playing backgammon is the owner of the hedgehog##1
2. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
4. the owner of the bird is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3     |
| Pet         | guinea-pig | bird     | hedgehog |
| Game   | scrabble        | canasta | backgammon    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-6::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: scientific, drama, comedy
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, motorbike, train
1. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
2. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person watching comedy movies is the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |   3   |
| Movie-Genre        | comedy | scientific      | drama  |
| Transport   | boat       | motorbike | train |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-7::.
3 different games are played: canasta, monopoly, backgammon
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, ferret, goldfish
1. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
2. the person playing monopoly is the owner of the ferret##1
3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3    |
| Game   | backgammon      | canasta     | monopoly    |
| Pet           | chinchilla | goldfish | ferret |

