.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-8::.
There 3 different types of food: asparagus, peach, pomegranate
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, fanta, coffee
1. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
2. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
3. the person eating peach is the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |
| Food    | pomegranate | asparagus | peach      |
| Beverage   | juice     | coffee | fanta |

