.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-11::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, punk, trance
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, go, whist
1. the fan of trance is the person playing mah-jongg##1
2. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the fan of punk##1
3. the person playing whist is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |
| Music-Genre   | classical | trance   | punk  |
| Game   | whist    | mah-jongg | go |

