2. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the brazilian##1
3. the egyptian is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Flower   | poppy    | daisy     | sunflower   |
| Nationality   | egyptian | brazilian | nigerian |

