1. the journalist is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
2. the person who growsiris is in the middle##1
3. the dressmaker is on the right of the person who growsiris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |       1       |     2      |     3      |
| Flower   | orchid     | iris   | begonia     |
| Job    | social-worker | journalist | dressmaker |

