1. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the security-guard##1
2. the security-guard is on the left of the electrician##1
3. the electrician is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |       2        |      3      |
| Job   | coach    | security-guard | electrician |
| Game   | scrabble | mah-jongg     | billiard        |

