.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-15::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, iced-tea, juice
The people have 3 different jobs:  lawyer, teacher, fisherman
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1
2. the fisherman is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the person drinking juice is on the right of the teacher##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |     3     |
| Beverage      | 7up  | juice | iced-tea  |
| Job   | teacher | fisherman   | lawyer |

