.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-18::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: photography, camping, dancing
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, skiing, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
2. the person who's hobby is photography is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
3. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2     |       3       |
| Hobby    | camping | dancing   | photography        |
| Sport   | skiing    | climbing | weightlifting |

